# Project Overview

This project is a modern marketplace platform connecting local farmers with buyers.

The platform focuses on:
- transparency
- trust
- local food
- video proof of farming practices
- authentic farmer identity

Farmers can:
- create profiles
- upload products
- upload photos and videos
- share farming methods
- explain fertilizers and production process
- receive ratings and reviews

Buyers can:
- browse products
- discover local farmers
- watch farming videos
- review farmers
- build trust through transparency

The platform should feel:
- modern
- organic
- trustworthy
- minimal
- mobile-first

# Tech Stack

Use:
- Next.js 15 App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Supabase

# Code Standards

Always:
- create reusable components
- keep components small
- separate UI from logic
- use TypeScript properly
- avoid duplicated code
- prefer server components when possible
- use clean folder structure
- use responsive design
- use accessible HTML

# Design System

Design should use:
- soft shadows
- rounded corners
- excellent spacing
- modern marketplace UI patterns
- calm organic aesthetic

Avoid:
- overly complex abstractions
- large files
- unnecessary dependencies
- messy state management

# Architecture

Prefer:
- feature-based organization
- reusable UI components
- scalable structure

# Important

Do NOT:
- generate huge files
- generate unnecessary code
- overengineer features
- implement features not requested

Always focus on:
- maintainability
- readability
- scalability